{"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"addGeoJSONSourceFeatures","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"forSourceId","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"sourceId"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"String","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"features"},{"text":": [","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/Feature-swift.typealias","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Feature","preciseIdentifier":"s:10MapboxMaps7Featurea"},{"text":"], ","kind":"text"},{"text":"dataId","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"String","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS"},{"text":"? = nil)","kind":"text"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The identifier of the style source."}]}],"name":"sourceId"},{"name":"features","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"An array of GeoJSON features to be added to the source.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"dataId","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An arbitrary string used to track the given GeoJSON data."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The add operation will be scheduled and applied on a GeoJSON serialization queue."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In order to capture events when actual data is drawn on the map please refer to Events API"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"and listen to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"onSourceDataLoaded"},{"type":"text","text":" (optionally pass the "},{"code":"dataId","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" parameter to filter the events)"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"onMapLoadingError"},{"text":" with ","type":"text"},{"code":"type = metadata","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" if data parsing error has occurred."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Partially updating a GeoJSON source is not compatible with using shared cache and generated IDs."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"It is important to ensure that every feature in the GeoJSON style source, as well as the newly added"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"feature, has a unique ID (or a unique promote ID if in use). Failure to provide unique IDs will result"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"in a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"map-loading-error"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The method allows the user to provide a data ID, which will be returned as the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"dataId"},{"text":" parameter in the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"source-data-loaded","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" event. However, it’s important to note that multiple partial updates can be queued","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"for the same GeoJSON source when ongoing source parsing is taking place. In these cases, the partial"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"updates will be applied to the source in batches. Only the data ID provided in the most recent call within"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"each batch will be included in the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"source-data-loaded"},{"text":" event. If no data ID is provided in the most recent","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"call, the data ID in the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"source-data-loaded"},{"type":"text","text":"event will be null."}]}],"name":"Note","style":"note"},{"style":"note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":""},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/StyleError","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" if there is a problem adding features to the source."}]}],"name":"Throws","type":"aside"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/StyleManager\/addGeoJSONSourceFeatures(forSourceId:features:dataId:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"MapboxMaps"}],"externalID":"s:10MapboxMaps12StyleManagerC24addGeoJSONSourceFeatures11forSourceId8features04dataK0ySS_Say4Turf7FeatureVGSSSgtF","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"addGeoJSONSourceFeatures","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"forSourceId"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"String","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"features","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": ["},{"text":"Feature","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10MapboxMaps7Featurea"},{"text":"], ","kind":"text"},{"text":"dataId","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","text":"String"},{"kind":"text","text":"?)"}],"title":"addGeoJSONSourceFeatures(forSourceId:features:dataId:)","roleHeading":"Instance Method","symbolKind":"method"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/mapboxmaps\/stylemanager\/addgeojsonsourcefeatures(forsourceid:features:dataid:)"]}],"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Add additional features to a GeoJSON style source."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps","doc:\/\/MapboxMa